  "postName": "2005-09-12-redesigninprogress",
  "html": "<p>Hi there.  If things around here are looking or acting a bit wonky, it's because I'm in the middle of my belated site overhaul I meant to do back in May.  It was preempted by <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/customer-reviews/0764597582/\">the book</a>, something about which I want to gush in detail very shortly.</p>\n<p>In between bouts of actually being busy, I've been yak shaving around the idea of executing this overhaul--making lists, researching sites I like, installing WordPress on my laptop.  Finally, after a bit of a weekend sprint during which I mangled the default theme a bit to my liking and installed a few plugins, I figured that I'd just throw the switch tonight and deal with the fallout as it arrives.</p>\n<p>For now, it's bedtime.  But, just for The Girl, here's me with the new book!</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.decafbad.com/2005/09/IMG_3562.JPG\" target=\"_new\"><img src=\"http://www.decafbad.com/2005/09/IMG_3562_th.JPG\" width=\"\" height=\"\"></a></p>\n<div id=\"comments\" class=\"comments archived-comments\"><h3>Archived Comments</h3>\n<ul class=\"comments\">\n<li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221088745\">\n<div class=\"meta\">\n<div class=\"author\">\n<a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://naeblis.cx/rtomayko/\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=abfc88b96ae18c85ba7aac3bded2ec5e&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"></a>\n<a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://naeblis.cx/rtomayko/\">Ryan Tomayko</a>\n</div>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"#comment-221088745\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-13T07:59:13\">2005-09-13T07:59:13</time></a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">Looks great!</div>\n\n\n</li>\n<li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221088746\">\n<div class=\"meta\">\n<div class=\"author\">\n<a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://rasterweb.net/raster/\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=db0fab74bcb564ebb09295498b892fb6&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"></a>\n<a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://rasterweb.net/raster/\">Pete Prodoehl</a>\n</div>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"#comment-221088746\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-13T11:23:34\">2005-09-13T11:23:34</time></a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">Awesome, now get back to posting on a regular basis! ;)</div>\n\n\n</li>\n<li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221088747\">\n<div class=\"meta\">\n<div class=\"author\">\n<a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.skippy.net/\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=1a320ac7f6818504df79fe42fc6b84a9&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"></a>\n<a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.skippy.net/\">skippy</a>\n</div>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"#comment-221088747\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-13T13:14:17\">2005-09-13T13:14:17</time></a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">Welcome to WordPress!  I've been reading your feed for ages, so I'm eager to see what you think of / do with WordPress.</div>\n\n\n</li>\n<li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221088749\">\n<div class=\"meta\">\n<div class=\"author\">\n<a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photomatt.net/\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=767fc9c115a1b989744c755db47feb60&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"></a>\n<a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photomatt.net/\">Matt</a>\n</div>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"#comment-221088749\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-13T18:39:02\">2005-09-13T18:39:02</time></a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">Welcome to the family. :)</div>\n\n\n</li>\n<li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221088750\">\n<div class=\"meta\">\n<div class=\"author\">\n<a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://advogato.org/person/mbrubeck/\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=85232f8499fd6ee91623408fc23835d1&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"></a>\n<a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://advogato.org/person/mbrubeck/\">Matt Brubeck</a>\n</div>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"#comment-221088750\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-16T15:46:57\">2005-09-16T15:46:57</time></a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">Where's are the links?  I see that the archives are back online at http://www.decafbad.com/links/ but there are no new links there.  Are they on del.icio.us somewhere?</div>\n\n\n</li>\n<li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221088751\">\n<div class=\"meta\">\n<div class=\"author\">\n<a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.decafbad.com\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=2377f34a68801b861c3e54e1301f0dce&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"></a>\n<a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.decafbad.com\">l.m.orchard</a>\n</div>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"#comment-221088751\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-16T15:50:56\">2005-09-16T15:50:56</time></a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">Matt:  Good question!  I'm taking baby steps around here, so for now the links section is stale.  My live links can be seen on del.icio.us here:\nhttp://del.icio.us/deusx\nBefore the weekend's out, though, I'm hoping to use an importer to pull my links into a category on this blog and try to reconstruct something of some semblance to the old links section.</div>\n\n\n</li>\n<li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221088752\">\n<div class=\"meta\">\n<div class=\"author\">\n<a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blog.nur-eine-i.de\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=e7368d797917d0df7942c26d4ed2e580&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"></a>\n<a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blog.nur-eine-i.de\">Benjamin Reitzammer</a>\n</div>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"#comment-221088752\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-21T10:41:12\">2005-09-21T10:41:12</time></a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">Thought I point it out ... your permalinks have changed slightly, for example from http://decafbad.com/blog/2005/07/18/ajax_testing_and_logging \nto \nhttp://www.decafbad.com/blog/2005/07/18/ajax-testing-and-logging\nThis is especially \"challenging\" because you simply shout \"Go away\" on decafbad.com instead of redirecting to decafbad.com/blog which seems like a natural alternative.</div>\n\n\n</li>\n<li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221088753\">\n<div class=\"meta\">\n<div class=\"author\">\n<a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blog.nur-eine-i.de\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=e7368d797917d0df7942c26d4ed2e580&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"></a>\n<a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blog.nur-eine-i.de\">Benjamin Reitzammer</a>\n</div>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"#comment-221088753\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-21T10:42:51\">2005-09-21T10:42:51</time></a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">Worpress messed up my previous comment ... the URLs differ in that the new URLs have dashes in the \"post titles\" while the old URLs had underscores ... sorry for double posting.</div>\n\n\n</li>\n<li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221088754\">\n<div class=\"meta\">\n<div class=\"author\">\n<a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.decafbad.com\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=2377f34a68801b861c3e54e1301f0dce&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"></a>\n<a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.decafbad.com\">l.m.orchard</a>\n</div>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"#comment-221088754\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-22T14:30:44\">2005-09-22T14:30:44</time></a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">Benjamin:  Ack!  Thanks for catching that - it's certainly not intentional and is a bug I need to fix.</div>\n\n\n</li>\n<li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221088755\">\n<div class=\"meta\">\n<div class=\"author\">\n<a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.decafbad.com\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=2377f34a68801b861c3e54e1301f0dce&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"></a>\n<a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.decafbad.com\">l.m.orchard</a>\n</div>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"#comment-221088755\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-22T14:34:43\">2005-09-22T14:34:43</time></a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">Yup, turns out it was a ServerName with a www where I didn't want one to be.  I *had* actually gone through the trouble to hack WordPress to replace underscores with dashes when looking up posts from permalinks until I'd whipped up a better mod_rewrite solution...</div>\n\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n",
  "body": "Hi there.  If things around here are looking or acting a bit wonky, it's because I'm in the middle of my belated site overhaul I meant to do back in May.  It was preempted by [the book][book], something about which I want to gush in detail very shortly.\r\n\r\nIn between bouts of actually being busy, I've been yak shaving around the idea of executing this overhaul--making lists, researching sites I like, installing WordPress on my laptop.  Finally, after a bit of a weekend sprint during which I mangled the default theme a bit to my liking and installed a few plugins, I figured that I'd just throw the switch tonight and deal with the fallout as it arrives.\r\n\r\nFor now, it's bedtime.  But, just for The Girl, here's me with the new book!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.decafbad.com/2005/09/IMG_3562.JPG\" target=\"_new\"><img src=\"http://www.decafbad.com/2005/09/IMG_3562_th.JPG\" /></a><br />\r\n\r\n[book]: http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/customer-reviews/0764597582/\n\n<div id=\"comments\" class=\"comments archived-comments\">\n            <h3>Archived Comments</h3>\n            \n        <ul class=\"comments\">\n            \n        <li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221088745\">\n            <div class=\"meta\">\n                <div class=\"author\">\n                    <a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" \n                       href=\"http://naeblis.cx/rtomayko/\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=abfc88b96ae18c85ba7aac3bded2ec5e&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\"/></a>\n                    <a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" \n                       href=\"http://naeblis.cx/rtomayko/\">Ryan Tomayko</a>\n                </div>\n                <a href=\"#comment-221088745\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-13T07:59:13\">2005-09-13T07:59:13</time></a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"content\">Looks great!</div>\n            \n        </li>